title: The Brujo - A Dynamic Force in Pirsig's Lila, in the World and Within Us
description:
The concept of the "brujo" helped Phaedrus conceptualize the shift in his Metaphysics of Quality from Describing the dichotomy of Classic and Romantic Quality to the Interplay of Static and Dynamic Quality. 

The Zuni Misfit was the Brujo for his community. Who are the Brujos for us? How can the Brujo help us live a Quality Existence? What is the interplay between static & Dynamic in today's journalism?
